"Believers," Part 5 of 5: The sense-shattering conclusion!

Reunited at last, Mulder and Scully pursue the Deacon deep beneath the surface of Yellowstone National Park. Also in pursuit are the telltale black helicopters of the FBI, but are they friend... or foe?
